hopobject.body: How much will it cost to send this letter to ? generic rogaine foam walmart "Frankly, it was the post-verdict press conference that Mark conducted where he challenged the media but also the judicial system itself. Those of us who watched that news conference said, 'Now there is a guy who spoke truth to power,' and we began to get the idea that perhaps he is somebody that we should honor with the Jefferson Cup for the way in which he took on the legal profession where he makes his living."
